{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<input type=\"reset\">","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></code>&nbsp;type 类型为 <strong><code>\"reset\"</code></strong>&nbsp;元素呈现为按钮，且带有默认的&nbsp;<code><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">click (en-US)</a></code></code>&nbsp;事件，用于将表单中的所有输入重置为其初始值。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/input-reset.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>您通常应该尽量避免在表单中包含重置按钮。 它们很少有实用性，事实上更有可能使用户误点而感到沮丧（通常是在尝试单击 “<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/submit\">提交</a>” 按钮时）。</p>\n</div>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"#值\">值</a></strong></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></code>用做按钮标签</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>事件</strong></td>\n   <td><code><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">click (en-US)</a></code></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>支持的常用属性</strong></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-type\"><code>type</code></a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-value\"><code>value</code></a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>IDL 属性</strong></td>\n   <td><code>value</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>方法</strong></td>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;input type=\"reset\"&gt;</code> 元素的&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-value\"><code>value</code></a></code>&nbsp;属性包含一个用做按钮标签的 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></code>，诸如 <code>reset</code>之类的按钮没有其他值。</p>\n\n<div id=\"summary-example3\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Reset the form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"summary-example3 sample\" id=\"frame_summary-example3\" width=\"650\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset/_sample_.summary-example3.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>如果您未指定 <code>value</code>，则会获得一个带有默认标签的按钮（通常为 “重置”，但这将根据 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">user agent</a> 而有所不同：</p>\n\n<div id=\"summary-example1\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"summary-example1 sample\" id=\"frame_summary-example1\" width=\"650\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset/_sample_.summary-example1.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用重置按钮","title":"使用重置按钮","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;input type =“ reset”&gt;</code>&nbsp;按钮用于重置表单。 如果您要创建自定义按钮，则使用 JavaScript 自定义行为，您需要使用&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/button\">&lt;input type=\"button\"&gt;</a></code>，或者最好使用&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a></code>&nbsp;元素。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一个简单的重置按钮","title":"一个简单的重置按钮","isH3":true,"content":"<p>我们将从创建一个简单的重置按钮开始：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Type in some sample text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Reset the form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>如下所示：</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"一个简单的重置按钮\" id=\"frame_a_simple_reset_button\" width=\"650\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset/_sample_.a_simple_reset_button.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>尝试在文本字段中输入一些文本，然后点击重置按钮。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"添加重置键盘快捷键","title":"添加重置键盘快捷键","isH3":true,"content":"<p>添加键盘快捷键到提交按钮 — 就像您使用&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></code> 一样做一些事情&nbsp;— 请使用 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-accesskey\"><code>accesskey</code></a></code>&nbsp;全局属性。</p>\n\n<p>在这个例子中，&nbsp;<kbd>r</kbd>&nbsp;被指定为访问键（您需要按&nbsp;<kbd>r</kbd>&nbsp;键与浏览器或操作系统的特定键相组合； 关于这些命令请参见&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-accesskey\"><code>accesskey</code></a></code>&nbsp;）。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Type in some sample text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Reset the form<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token attr-name\">accesskey</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"添加重置键盘快捷键\" id=\"frame_adding_a_reset_keyboard_shortcut\" width=\"650\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset/_sample_.adding_a_reset_keyboard_shortcut.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>上面的示例的问题在于，用户无法知道访问键是什么！事实上，是因为修饰符通常是非标准的以避免与系统和软件快捷键冲突。&nbsp;在构建网站时，请确保以不干扰网站设计的方式提供此信息（例如，通过提供易于访问的链接来指向有关网站访问键的信息）。向按钮添加提示（也可以使用&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a></code> 属性）, 尽管这并不是出于可访问性目的的完善的解决方案。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"禁用和启用重置按钮","title":"禁用和启用重置按钮","isH3":true,"content":"<p>要禁用重置按钮，只需在其上指定 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-disabled\"><code>disabled</code></a></code>&nbsp;的全局属性，如下所示：</p>\n\n<div id=\"disable-example1\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Disabled<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">disabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>您可以在运行时通过简单地将 <code>disable</code> 设置为 <code>true</code> 或 <code>false</code> 来启用和禁用按钮。在 JavaScript 中，使用<code>btn.disabled = true</code>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<code>btn.disabled = false</code>。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p>注意：有关启用和禁用按钮的更多想法，请参见&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/button#disabling_and_enabling_a_button\">&lt;input type=\"button\"&gt;</a></code>&nbsp;页面。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"验证方式","title":"<strong>验证方式</strong>","isH3":false,"content":"<p>按钮并不参与约束性验证；他们并没有实际的约束价值。</p>","titleAsText":"验证方式"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>我们在上面已经提供了一些简单的示例。 实际上关于重置按钮并没有更多的内容了。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术规格","title":"技术规格","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>规范</td>\n   <td>状态</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#reset-button-state-(type=reset)\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;input type=\"reset\"&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/forms.html#reset-button-state-(type=reset)\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;input type=\"reset\"&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.input.input-reset","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a> 实现接口</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Forms_and_buttons\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Forms and buttons</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms\">Forms (accessibility)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms\">HTML forms</a></li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a> element</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"值","id":"值"},{"text":"使用重置按钮","id":"使用重置按钮"},{"text":"<strong>验证方式</strong>","id":"验证方式"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"技术规格","id":"技术规格"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"<input> type 类型为 \"reset\" 元素呈现为按钮，且带有默认的 click (en-US) 事件，用于将表单中的所有输入重置为其初始值。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<input type=\"reset\">","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<input type=\"reset\">","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<input type=\"reset\">","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/input/reset","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/input/reset/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input","title":"<input>：输入（表单输入）元素"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input/reset","title":"<input type=\"reset\">"}],"pageTitle":"<input type=\"reset\"> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}